title: Bug 121170: get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: The labels returned by the 'get column label' function are null before extraction, while after extraction they are recognizable strings.
EB: The 'get column label' function should return the same labels before extraction as it does after extraction. These labels should be user recognizable strings that can be displayed to the end user.
SR: To reproduce the issue, perform an extraction using the meta data object and note the labels returned by the 'get column label' function before and after extraction.
